mysql_groundtruth: SELECT ROUND(SUM(DAILY_AVG)/COUNT(*) *100, 2) AS AVERAGE_DAILY_PERCENT FROM (SELECT A.ACTION_DATE, COUNT( DISTINCT R.POST_ID)/COUNT(DISTINCT A.POST_ID) AS DAILY_AVG FROM ACTIONS AS A LEFT JOIN REMOVALS AS R ON A.POST_ID = R.POST_ID WHERE A.ACTION='report' AND A.EXTRA='spam' GROUP BY ACTION_DATE) AS TEMP
